{"tid":2146163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"敏感時期 李克強再次硬推「地攤經濟」","createTime":"2020-08-08T11:47:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T01:27:48.000Z","uid":184679,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0894f29cec2a9378fcd18936ef44ae5df723dcf4","tid":2146163,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T11:47:00.000Z","msg":"中共七常委連續七天沒有公開露面，照慣例應是正在北戴河舉行秘密會議。在此敏感時期，中共國務院出臺文件，鼓勵發展「個體經濟」，被指是「地攤經濟」的翻版。有分析認為，李克強此時硬推「地攤經濟」，既反映出中國經濟和就業問題的艱難處境，也凸顯習李之間的路線鬥爭再次激化。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ntdtv.com/assets/uploads/2020/08/GettyImages-1226156576-2-600x338.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ntdtv.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2FGettyImages-1226156576-2-600x338.jpg&h=656d510d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（Andrea Verdelli/Getty Images）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2020/08/08/a102913426.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2020%2F08%2F08%2Fa102913426.html&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW%2F7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=c5190a6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2020/08/08/a102913426.html</a>"},{"pid":"0b8e2085889125d93fc5eee6a32cdc7ba2153b0d","tid":2146163,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T00:40:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YPkwJ4sGvnU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYPkwJ4sGvnU&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW%2F7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=7a45c3aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YPkwJ4sGvnU</a>"},{"pid":"aa451fef943c1d881774126be07920a1965dbf4e","tid":2146163,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T01:07:10.000Z","msg":"白卡習玩撚到一大堆公司摺左<br />\n工都無得開<br />\n<br />\n係可以去擺地攤,但咩水比錢買野"},{"pid":"0cdb99307141f23c0e984a6dadbe5729e0c7daec","tid":2146163,"uid":330227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T01:27:48.000Z","msg":"<i